  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study intends to solve the following problems: whether use dexamethasone can obviously
      decrease transplant cancelling probability in fresh embryo transplant cycle or not, reduce
      time and frequency going to hospital repeatedly for patients need frozen embryo transplant or
      not, and reduce the economic burden for patients or not; By comparing pregnancy rate of
      single transplant, hope to make clear in IVF-ET treatment for patients progesterone increases
      to a certain level whether it is a good choice to transfer fresh embryo after dexamethasone
      treatment, or frozen embryo transplant is better.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
